metadata.title: Resolute
metadata.description:
Resolute is the genesis landscape NFT from First Man.

This little tree stands resolute on the banks of one of the largest lakes in the English Lake District. This was the day I discovered the tree and was amazed as it sat submerged after weeks of solid rain. It is difficult not to be inspired by the location, not only for the hardiness of tree, but also the imposing and ancient mountains that watch over it.

The original collector receives a fine art print.
